PrecisAmendments to the HEALTH OF ANIMALS REGULATIONS dealing with the importation and disposal of garbage or waste containing animal matter, such as the kind brought by aircraft or ships en route to Canada, and revoking the provisions pertaining to the maximum amount of compensation that is payable under the Act for animals that are destroyed by order.
